00:33:29.450 --> 00:33:31.270
Well to describe uranium,

887
00:33:31.270 --> 00:33:33.710
we have to write the wave function of uranium

888
00:33:33.710 --> 00:33:35.269
which is disintegrated,

889
00:33:35.269 --> 00:33:37.469
and uranium which hasn't disintegrated.

890
00:33:37.469 --> 00:33:40.249
50% chance maybe that it'll disintegrate,

891
00:33:40.249 --> 00:33:42.970
50% chance that it hasn't disintegrated,

892
00:33:42.970 --> 00:33:45.240
that's the quantum theory.

893
00:33:45.470 --> 00:33:47.150
You're working on probabilities, right?

894
00:33:47.150 --> 00:33:49.009
The atomic bomb is based on this theory.

895
00:33:49.009 --> 00:33:50.490
The atomic bomb wouldn't work,

896
00:33:50.490 --> 00:33:52.350
