00:33:52.350 --> 00:33:55.810
But now hook the uranium to a gun,

898
00:33:55.810 --> 00:33:57.960
well is the cat dead or alive?

899
00:33:58.630 --> 00:34:02.309
Well, you have to add the wave function of a dead cat

900
00:34:02.309 --> 00:34:04.009
