901
00:34:04.009 --> 00:34:06.389
of a life cat, simultaneously,

902
00:34:06.389 --> 00:34:09.319
so the cat is neither dead or alive.

903
00:34:09.509 --> 00:34:10.849
Now you may say to yourself,

904
00:34:10.849 --> 00:34:12.389
